title: Ep. - 411 - TYLER BALTIERRA FROM TEEN MOM OG JEN SHAH FRAUD CHARGES AND ARREST
description:
Tyler Baltierra from MTV’s Teen Mom OG discusses this week’s emotional episode, which featured Tyler and Catelynn reuniting with their daughter Carly whom they placed for adoption in 2009. Tyler and Catelynn are now married with three additional daughters.

 

Kate discusses this week’s Real Housewives of Salt Lake City episode with attorney David Fleck, an expert on fraud.
